{
  "abstract": "This report presents the value chain analysis for pigeonpeas in the South-eastern Tanzania. The study is part of the ICRISAT project “Enhancing Productivity of Groundnut and Pigeon pea Cropping Systems in Eastern Africa”. Specifically, it forms part of Output 3: Structure, conduct and performance of value chains for groundnut and pigeon pea. In this output includes two activities: firstly Map existing value chains and identify constraints on market performance and secondly test innovations to enhance performance of the value chain.",
